import { Button, Form } from "react-bootstrap"

export const SearchBar=()=> {
  return (
   <>
   <Form >
         <Form.Group >
           <Form.Control type='text' placeholder="Enter your City ...."></Form.Control>  
              </Form.Group>   
        <Form.Group >
           <Form.Control type='text' placeholder="Enter your City ...."></Form.Control>  
              <Button variant="primary" >Search</Button>
        </Form.Group>              
   </Form>
   </>
  )
}
